    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aium</ex></expan> Marium <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilium</ex></expan> lega</supplied>tum Alexandreae Italicei quei fuere <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">virtut</supplied>is beneficique ergo </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ἀγασίας Μηνοφίλου <lb n="2"/>Ἐφέσιος ἐποίει </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Γάιον Μάριον πρεσβευ</supplied>τὴν οἱ ἐν Ἀλεξανδρείαι <supplied reason="lost">παρα</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">γενόμενοι Ἰταλικ</supplied>οὶ ἀρετῆς καὶ εὐεργεσίας <supplied reason="lost">ἕνεκα</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht aus zwei Fragmenten. Die Maße des kleineren Fragments sind: Höhe: 25.5; Breite: -102; Tiefe: 36.5.</p>
            </div>
